/***********************************************/
/* jdime  -  Structured Merge with Auto-Tuning */
/***********************************************/

System Requirements: 
  o rcs (http://www.gnu.org/software/rcs/)
  o glpk (http://www.gnu.org/software/glpk/)
  o gplk-java (http://glpk-java.sourceforge.net/)

  Debian/Ubuntu: apt-get install rcs glpk libglpk-java
  Redhat/Fedora: yum install rcs glpk
                 glpk-java has to be installed manually
  Suse/OpenSuse: zypper install rcs glpk
                 glpk-java has to be installed manually

Note: The path to glpk-java in the shellscript 'jdime' has to be modfied 
      according to your system configuration!